"title": "5627: word",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5627",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ is described as God's word. The word encompassed the promise of God and the gospel and is a help in trial and temptation. Human beings should use words wisely.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ and God's word</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ described as the Word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1-John1:3\">JHN 1:1–1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:2\">HEB 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1-1John1:2\">1JN 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:13\">REV 19:13</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ preaches the word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:2\">MRK 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:29\">MAT 7:24–7:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:47-Luke6:49\">LUK 6:47–6:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:20-Matt13:23\">MAT 13:20–13:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:13-Mark4:20\">MRK 4:13–4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:11-Luke8:15\">LUK 8:11–8:15</a> <em>the parable of the sower</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:28\">LUK 11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:34\">JHN 3:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:63-John6:68\">JHN 6:63–6:68</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:31-John8:32\">JHN 8:31–8:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:47\">JHN 8:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:52\">JHN 8:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:47-John12:50\">JHN 12:47–12:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:10-John14:24\">JHN 14:10–14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:3\">JHN 15:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6-John17:8\">JHN 17:6–17:8</a></p>\n<h2>The word and the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">ACT 4:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:29\">ACT 4:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:44-Acts13:46\">ACT 13:44–13:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:10\">ACT 19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:24\">ACT 20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:14\">DEU 30:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:8-Rom10:10\">ROM 10:8–10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:5\">COL 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:2\">HEB 4:2</a></p>\n<h2>God's word is a promise and help in trial and temptation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:9-Ps119:11\">PSA 119:9–119:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:4-Ps33:5\">PSA 33:4–33:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:105\">PSA 119:105</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:133\">PSA 119:133</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:4\">MAT 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23-John14:24\">JHN 14:23–14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:17\">JHN 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:17\">EPH 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:12\">HEB 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:3\">1JN 5:3</a></p>\n<h2>Words should be used wisely</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:36-Matt12:37\">MAT 12:36–12:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:1-Judg8:3\">JDG 8:1–8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:13-2Chr10:14\">2CH 10:13–10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:19\">PRO 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:18\">PRO 12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:25\">PRO 12:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:1\">PRO 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:24\">PRO 16:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:15\">PRO 25:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:11\">ECC 12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:1-Jas3:12\">JAS 3:1–3:12</a></p>",
